<h1><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>About <%= defaults.application.name %></h1>

<div class="content">
	<p><%= defaults.application.name %> is a web based utility that allows search the University of Wisconsin community. </p>

	<div class="details section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Features</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Search by text, URL, or PDF file.</li>
					<li>Search for authors or articles .</li>
					<li>Weight results by # of relevant publications.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-star"></i>Benefits</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Get to know your colleagues.</li>
					<li>Understand research at UW-Madison.</li>
					<li>Helps to conduct your own research.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h2><i class="fa fa-desktop"></i>Screen Shots</h2>

	<div class="figure">
		<a href="images/info/desktop-search.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="<%= defaults.application.name %>"><img src="images/info/desktop-search.png" /></a>
		<div class="caption"><%= defaults.application.name %></div>
	</div>

	<div class="figure row">
		<div class="figure">
			<img src="images/info/iphone-search.png" style="border:none; width:300px" />
			<div class="caption"><%= defaults.application.name %> Mobile</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>